      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/biden-campaign-co-chair-warns-donor-cash-drying-up-semafor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Semafor 援引知情人士透露，好莱坞大亨、乔·拜登连任竞选团队联合主席杰弗里·卡森伯格告诉总统，捐助者的耐心已经耗尽。]]></description>
